Commands
Add VLANs

Creates missing VLANs and adds them to trunks.

python addvlansv14.py --switches switches.txt --vlans vlans.csv --verbose

Remove VLANs (Full Cleanup)

Removes VLANs from trunks, deletes SVI if present, then deletes VLAN globally.

python addvlansv14.py --switches switches.txt --vlans vlans.csv \
--remove --delete-svi --delete-vlans-global --verbose --verify

Dry Run

Preview changes without modifying devices.

python addvlansv14.py --switches switches.txt --vlans vlans.csv --dry-run --verbose

Important Behavior

VLANs remain in show vlan unless --delete-vlans-global is used

